at automated decision making and/or profiling we do with user data</h3>\r\n<h3>Industry regulatory disclosure requirements</h3>', 'Privacy Policy', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '3-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-08-19 14:02:01', '2018-08-19 06:02:01', '', 3, 'http://tianyan.local/3-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
